sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant OnlineFS as Feature Server (Online)<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Registry as Registry Service<br/>6570/TCP gRPC
    participant Transform as Transformation Service<br/>6569/TCP gRPC
    participant OnlineStore as Online Store<br/>(Redis 6379/TCP or PostgreSQL 5432/TCP)
    participant OfflineStore as Offline Store<br/>(BigQuery/Snowflake 443/TCP HTTPS)

    Note over MLApp,OnlineStore: Flow 1: Real-Time Feature Retrieval

    MLApp->>OnlineFS: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (Optional)
    OnlineFS->>Registry: GetFeatureView()<br/>gRPC (unencrypted)
    Registry-->>OnlineFS: Feature metadata
    OnlineFS->>OnlineStore: Get feature values<br/>TLS Optional, Password Auth
    OnlineStore-->>OnlineFS: Feature data
    OnlineFS->>Transform: TransformFeatures()<br/>gRPC (unencrypted)
    Transform-->>OnlineFS: Transformed features
    OnlineFS-->>MLApp: JSON response with features

    Note over MLApp,OfflineStore: Flow 2: Feature Materialization (Offline to Online)

    MLApp->>OnlineFS: POST /materialize<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    OnlineFS->>OfflineStore: Query historical features<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Cloud IAM
    OfflineStore-->>OnlineFS: Historical feature data
    OnlineFS->>OnlineStore: Write features<br/>TLS Optional, Password
    OnlineStore-->>OnlineFS: Acknowledgment
    OnlineFS-->>MLApp: Materialization complete

    Note over MLApp,OfflineStore: Flow 3: Feature Push (Streaming)

    participant StreamApp as Stream Processing App
    StreamApp->>OnlineFS: POST /push<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    OnlineFS->>OnlineStore: Write features<br/>TLS Optional, Password
    OnlineStore-->>OnlineFS: Acknowledgment
    OnlineFS->>OfflineStore: Write to offline (optional)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Cloud IAM
    OfflineStore-->>OnlineFS: Acknowledgment
    OnlineFS-->>StreamApp: Push complete
